<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 06:17:09 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>哈马斯在与巴勒斯坦对手法塔赫的会谈中展现了战后雄心</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/hamas-signals-post-war-ambition-talks-with-palestinian-rival-fatah-2024-06-05/</link><description>与哈马斯和法塔赫这两个巴勒斯坦派系的五名消息人士的对话表明，本月巴勒斯坦派系哈马斯和法塔赫之间的深刻分歧将限制其和解谈判的进展，但会议强调，在以色列加沙战争后，伊斯兰组织可能会保留影响力。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 06:06:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/hamas-signals-post-war-ambition-talks-with-palestinian-rival-fatah-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>Zara 母公司 Inditex 报告季度销售增长放缓</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/zara-owner-inditex-reports-slowing-quarterly-sales-growth-2024-06-05/</link><description>Zara 母公司 Inditex 周三表示，其财年第一季度销售额增长了 7%，符合分析师的预期。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 05:38:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/zara-owner-inditex-reports-slowing-quarterly-sales-growth-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>独家：电动汽车制造商蔚来获得中国第三家工厂的监管许可</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/ev-maker-nio-gets-regulatory-nod-third-factory-china-sources-say-2024-06-05/</link><description>三名知情人士表示，电动汽车制造商蔚来汽车已获得在中国建设第三家工厂的批准，这将使其批准的总产能提高到 100 万辆汽车，几乎与特斯拉庞大的上海工厂持平。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 05:28:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/ev-maker-nio-gets-regulatory-nod-third-factory-china-sources-say-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>在另一位临时教练的带领下，韩国有望在 2026 年预选赛中晋级</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/with-another-interim-coach-helm-south-korea-look-advance-2026-qualifiers-2024-06-05/</link><description>尽管金道勋成为自今年年初以来第三位执掌亚洲重量级球队的教练，但韩国周四将迎战新加坡，只需一分即可确保晋级 2026 年世界杯亚洲区预选赛第三轮。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 04:13:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/with-another-interim-coach-helm-south-korea-look-advance-2026-qualifiers-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市因降息押注而上涨，印度市场波动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-06-05/</link><description>亚洲股市周三普遍上涨，而美元则保持稳定，原因是美国劳动力市场疲软，强化了美联储 9 月降息的预期，且投资者等待本周晚些时候重要的非农就业报告。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 02:52:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>在银行诈骗中损失金钱的中国人抗议后被拘留数月</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-who-lost-money-bank-fraud-detained-months-after-protest-2024-06-05/</link><description>该报道基于路透社对抗议录像、此前未报道的逮捕通知和采访的回顾，审视了自 2022 年以来在中国激增的一场经济抗议活动，在此期间，数十万人在房地产泡沫破裂中失去了房屋并成为受害者到投资诈骗。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 02:04:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-who-lost-money-bank-fraud-detained-months-after-protest-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>财新PMI显示，中国强劲的服务业活动拉动就业</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-robust-services-activity-drives-up-employment-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-06-05/</link><description>周三的一项私营部门调查显示，中国 5 月份服务业活动以 10 个月来最快速度加速，人员配备水平自 1 月份以来首次扩大，表明第二季度将持续复苏。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 01:49:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-robust-services-activity-drives-up-employment-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查：投资者考虑选举和美国潜在宽松政策，新兴货币并未获得缓解</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/no-relief-emerging-currencies-seen-investors-ponder-elections-potential-us-2024-06-05/</link><description>路透对货币分析师的调查显示，由于美联储不急于降息以及一些关键的全国大选结果，新兴市场货币今年将难以反弹。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 01:38:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/no-relief-emerging-currencies-seen-investors-ponder-elections-potential-us-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>加拿大央行考虑降息，美元站稳脚跟</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-finds-footing-traders-turn-us-services-data-2024-06-05/</link><description>在加拿大召开政策会议之前，美元周三企稳，交易员押注全球一些最大经济体将开始降息周期。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 00:47:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-finds-footing-traders-turn-us-services-data-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>SEKO 赢得美国海关机构有条件恢复</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/seko-wins-conditional-reinstatements-us-customs-agency-2024-06-05/</link><description>私营公司SEKO Logistics表示，美国海关与边境保护局（CBP）已有条件恢复其对两个重要国际贸易项目的参与，但仍未确定导致暂停的违规行为。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 00:29:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/seko-wins-conditional-reinstatements-us-customs-agency-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国人工智能芯片公司降级设计以确保台积电生产</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinese-ai-chip-firms-downgrading-designs-secure-tsmc-production-sources-say-2024-06-04/</link><description>四位知情人士表示，一些中国人工智能芯片公司现在正在设计功能较弱的处理器，以在面临美国制裁的情况下保留台积电的生产权。</description><pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 23:03:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinese-ai-chip-firms-downgrading-designs-secure-tsmc-production-sources-say-2024-06-04/</guid></item><item><title>早间买盘：政治、市场波动刺激市场上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-06-04/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 21:52:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-06-04/</guid></item><item><title>格兰霍姆称美国对中国汽车征收更高的关税对汽车制造商至关重要</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/granholm-says-new-tariffs-chinese-vehicles-crucial-us-auto-industry-2024-06-04/</link><description>美国能源部长詹妮弗·格兰霍姆周二表示，8月份按计划将中国电动汽车进口关税翻两番至100%以上，这对美国汽车行业的健康至关重要。</description><pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 21:05:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/granholm-says-new-tariffs-chinese-vehicles-crucial-us-auto-industry-2024-06-04/</guid></item><item><title>美国参议员曼钦鼓励业界就电动汽车税收抵免起诉财政部</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-sen-manchin-says-hes-encouraging-industry-sue-treasury-over-ev-tax-credits-2024-06-04/</link><description>美国参议员乔·曼钦 (Joe Manchin) 周二表示，他敦促美国公司就财政部根据《通货膨胀削减法案》(IRA) 为获得清洁能源税收抵免的公司制定的本地含量规则提起诉讼。</description><pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 20:07:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-sen-manchin-says-hes-encouraging-industry-sue-treasury-over-ev-tax-credits-2024-06-04/</guid></item><item><title>克里姆林宫对土耳其加入金砖国家的愿望表示欢迎</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/kremlin-welcomes-turkeys-reported-desire-join-brics-2024-06-04/</link><description>克里姆林宫发言人德米特里·佩斯科夫周二表示，俄罗斯欢迎土耳其希望成为金砖国家集团成员的愿望，并称该主题将列入该组织下次峰会的议程。</description><pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 12:06:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/kremlin-welcomes-turkeys-reported-desire-join-brics-2024-06-04/</guid></item></channel></rss>